experiment NI_sodium
instrument VHF
start 2018 02 20 0000
end 2018 02 20 0400
status R
description The VHF radar (vertical) with the sodium lidar
contact Toru Takahashi
email takahashi.toru@nipr.ac.jp
operator Toru Takahashi
submitter Satonori NOZAWA
resources NI(14)
notes
We will conduct the electron density observation in the vertical
direction by EISCAT VHF radar (manda) with the high speed
observation of the sodium lidar to investigate the sodium density
depletion harmonized with the electron density enhancement due to
the pulsating aurora.
We will run the SP only when it is clear sky and geomagnetic
condition is active.
